## This install's file-reference prefix

For THIS install, the project prefix is **`<project-folder-name>/`** (the repo folder name).

Use this prefix in EVERY markdown link and backtick path in chat responses (per the framework's "File references in chat responses" rule):

```
[bear-den MANIFEST](<project-folder-name>/_context/bear-den/MANIFEST.md)
Reference to `<project-folder-name>/bear-watch/code/src/server/index.ts:1234`
```

Why this prefix: all active Claude Code sessions launch with a specific `cwd`. The preview pane resolves paths relative to that cwd. Bare-relative `_context/...` fails silently — needs the prefix to resolve correctly.

