## Canonical paths for this install

- **Repo:** `<absolute-path-to-repo>` *(local-only / has-remote — pick one)*
- **Data dir:** `<repo>/runtime/bots/` (env: `<INSTALL>_BOTS_DATA_DIR`, fallback `~/.<install>-bots/`)
- **Config dir:** `<repo>/runtime/config/` (env: `<INSTALL>_BOTS_HOME`)
- **pm2 daemon:** `<repo>/runtime/pm2/` (env: `PM2_HOME`)
- **Lab dir:** `<repo>/runtime/lab/` (env: `<INSTALL>_LAB_HOME`)
- **pm2 app names:** `bear-watch-server-<install-suffix>`, `paper-trade-bot-<install-suffix>`
- **Scheduled tasks:** `<INSTALL>-HealthCheck`, `<INSTALL>-WeatherPull`, etc. (`<INSTALL>-` prefix)
- **HTTP port:** `<port>`
- **Env var prefix:** `<INSTALL>_*`

