## Forbidden runtime paths

Per framework: never manually Write/Edit files under `runtime/` directories. For THIS install:

- `<this-install>/runtime/bots/` (and the fallback `~/.<install>-bots/`)
- `<this-install>/runtime/lab/` (and the fallback `~/.<install>-lab/`)
- `<this-install>/runtime/config/` (and the fallback `~/.<install>-config/`)
- `<this-install>/runtime/pm2/`

API endpoints that legitimately write to these locations as part of normal operation are fine. The rule blocks YOU from editing those files directly via Write/Edit tools.

