## Live state quick-check commands (for this install)

```powershell
# Bot server health
curl http://localhost:<port>/health

# pm2 process list (expect: bear-watch-server-<install-suffix>, paper-trade-bot-<install-suffix>, pm2-logrotate)
pm2 list

# Scheduled tasks (expect <INSTALL>-* tasks)
Get-ScheduledTask -TaskName "<INSTALL>-*" | Get-ScheduledTaskInfo | Select TaskName, LastRunTime, LastTaskResult
```

